⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Master Sword
node ZEL · ZEL · ⟦The Master Sword:ZEL:cf15ab⟧

WHO   — The Master Sword — the Blade of Evil's Bane
WHAT  — The Blade of Evil's Bane — a holy, evil-banishing sword that can seal Ganon and pierce the powers of darkness; only the chosen hero may wield it, and in his hand it shines.
WHERE — ZEL · The Legend of Zelda  Framework inputs: The Legend of Zelda (the saga entire)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because evil that cannot be slain by mortal steel must be sealed by a sacred edge; because the goddess foresaw the dark's return and forged a blade to meet it in every age.
HOW   — By a power that grows with the spirit of the one who bears it — banishing shadow, breaking curses, and rising sharpest against the very darkness it was made to oppose.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the blade that banishes evil — drawn only by the worthy, raised in every age against the dark.

